elements.name: Como usuario me registro y creo un post

steps.name: I enter to the setup page v "<SETUP_VALUES_REMOTE>" and take a screenshot for version "v3.42" feature "crear-post" scenario "1" step "1"
I click in the add post button v and take a screenshot for version "v3.42" feature "crear-post" scenario "1" step "2"
I enter a title for the post "<POST_TITLE>" v and take a screenshot for version "v3.42" feature "crear-post" scenario "1" step "3"
I enter a description for the post "<POST_DESCRIPTION>" v and take a screenshot for version "v3.42" feature "crear-post" scenario "1" step "4"
I click publish post button v and take a screenshot for version "v3.42" feature "crear-post" scenario "1" step "5"
I click publish post confirm button v and take a screenshot for version "v3.42" feature "crear-post" scenario "1" step "6"
I go back to dashboard v and take a screenshot for version "v3.42" feature "crear-post" scenario "1" step "7"
